{"tid":2070180,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"（警世POST）應承我，攞左一萬蚊唔好係香港消費","createTime":"2020-06-19T03:01:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T01:22:13.000Z","uid":213877,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8100cba7bdf138051c22082bf5ae57ec998cf655","tid":2070180,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T03:01:30.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，香港再出發大聯盟<br />\n<br />\n要明剃你眼眉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cfa00471becc505f756ae47841af5d43b03e999","tid":2070180,"uid":213877,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T03:02:22.000Z","msg":"再出發大聯盟發起「促消費」行動 設商戶優惠資訊平台<br />\n<br />\n政府1萬元現金發放計劃即將於 6 月 21 日（父親節）當日開始接受登記，並在 7 月 8 日起陸續「派錢」。<br />\n「香港再出發大聯盟」今日（11日）發起「促消費、撐經濟」行動，向全港商戶收集折扣及其他優惠資訊，同時聯絡全港各商場業主，希望他們推出優惠計劃拉動消費。<br />\n<br />\n大聯盟刺激消費促經濟小組召集人王惠貞表示，今次行動籌備僅兩星期，剛好趕及政府向全港市民發放一萬元現金之際，相信各大商場及商戶同事會有優惠政策推出，惟推銷渠道不足，希望全港商戶能充分利用其統一平台，把折扣和優惠放上網站。<br />\n<br />\n大聯盟副秘書長、香港中華出入口商會副會長黃英豪指，今次優惠資訊平台是開放式，絕對沒有任何「黃藍」標籤，但商戶需要透過商會提供的密碼登入網上戶口發放資訊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港餐飲聯業協會會長黃家和指過去數月限聚令打擊飲食業，業內失業率由去年3%上升至5月份的12%，餐飲及零售行業將舉辦更多宣傳推廣活促進經濟。他透露初步估計有逾千間食肆參與優惠活動，呼籲市民多外出消費。<br />\n<br />\n大聯盟發起人之一的藝人鍾鎮濤表示，對演藝界而言，社會穩定才會歌舞昇平，「限聚令最多准8個人，但要8千人先開得成演唱會，未有咁快可以同大家開Band唱歌。」表示會盡量多聘請樂手練歌，幫助行內經濟。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/政情/484644/再出發大聯盟發起-促消費-行動-設商戶優惠資訊平台\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85%2F484644%2F%E5%86%8D%E5%87%BA%E7%99%BC%E5%A4%A7%E8%81%AF%E7%9B%9F%E7%99%BC%E8%B5%B7-%E4%BF%83%E6%B6%88%E8%B2%BB-%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95-%E8%A8%AD%E5%95%86%E6%88%B6%E5%84%AA%E6%83%A0%E8%B3%87%E8%A8%8A%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84CwZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=bd16ce7c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/政情/484644/再出發大聯盟發起-促消費-行動-設商戶優惠資訊平台</a>"},{"pid":"b20cd3e99a6d549aeb30b7978ea0104a7ba16d7a","tid":2070180,"uid":213877,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T03:02:51.000Z","msg":"再出發大聯盟，謀住各位1萬蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42891d4d85625ed422641f1156d57aa3ff981a9a","tid":2070180,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T03:05:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1b92a5588db68e960cb3e04fe6fa5529b43fef2","tid":2070180,"uid":144084,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T03:06:31.000Z","msg":"買美股<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0a5301f7bdc4ac0f4c560bb4e7098048532053e","tid":2070180,"uid":213877,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"42891d4d85625ed422641f1156d57aa3ff981a9a","tid":2070180,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T03:05:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T03:08:23.000Z","msg":"鳩SIR，你好"},{"pid":"e44fe8770d62fd3b5939594f2062ff6bc264c165","tid":2070180,"uid":54516,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T03:09:56.000Z","msg":"再出殯個list得個五十幾間，一入自動標籤做藍店。除非有背景，呢個搵鬼入？"},{"pid":"b7c1043f7d54b4103d6eb57ea3c1ef4f6d842f12","tid":2070180,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T04:30:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52f7f1da1308990ecb22b2229b5ddab6d964f8df","tid":2070180,"uid":288312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T04:56:37.000Z","msg":"[法律戰線救手足] 打甩暴動罪!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2070225\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/20